<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head><%- include('../partials/head', { title }) %></head>
<body class="page-partner">
<%- include('../partials/header', { activePage }) %>

<main class="partner-main">
  <section class="partner-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="partner-hero-inner">
        <span class="partner-pill">Join The Mission</span>
        <h1>Partner With Moovex</h1>
        <p class="partner-lead">
          Empowering Zambian entrepreneurs with the tools, guidance, and ecosystem connections needed to
          thrive in a modern economy.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="partner-hero-photo" role="img" aria-label="Zambian entrepreneurs collaborating in a bright incubator space"></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="partner-why">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Why Support Our Ecosystem?</h2>
      <div class="partner-why-grid">
        <article class="partner-why-card partner-glass-card partner-soft-shadow">
          <div class="partner-why-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M22.7 19l-9.1-9.1c.9-2.3.4-5-1.5-6.9-2-2-5-2.4-7.4-1.3L9 6 6 9 1.6 4.7C.4 7.1.9 10.1 2.9 12.1c1.9 1.9 4.6 2.4 6.9 1.5l9.1 9.1c.4.4 1 .4 1.4 0l2.3-2.3c.5-.4.5-1.1.1-1.4z"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3>Practical Tools</h3>
            <p>We provide more than just theory. Our partners help deliver tangible guidance, digital tools, and logistical support directly to growing Zambian businesses.</p>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="partner-why-card partner-glass-card partner-soft-shadow">
          <div class="partner-why-icon partner-why-icon-green" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M17 8C8 10 5.9 16.17 3.82 21.34L5.71 22l1.02-2.44C8.14 18.04 10.79 17 13 17c5 0 8 3 8 8h2c0-6.08-4.42-10.42-9.33-11.3C14.5 12.5 15.5 11 17 8z"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3>Sustainability First</h3>
            <p>Support focuses on long-term infrastructure. We build local hubs that become self-sustaining engines of regional entrepreneurship growth.</p>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="partner-why-card partner-glass-card partner-soft-shadow">
          <div class="partner-why-icon partner-why-icon-orange" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M16 6l2.29 2.29-4.88 4.88-4-4L2 16.59 3.41 18l6-6 4 4 6.3-6.29L22 12V6h-6z"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3>Measured Growth</h3>
            <p>Transparency is our core value. Partnership support is tied to practical impact goals across the Moovex entrepreneurship ecosystem.</p>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="partner-impact-areas">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Where Your Impact Goes</h2>
      <div class="partner-impact-grid">
        <article class="partner-impact-tile partner-soft-shadow">
          <div class="partner-impact-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M5 13.18v4L12 21l7-3.82v-4L12 17l-7-3.82zM12 3L1 9l11 6 9-4.91V17h2V9L12 3z"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <span>Training</span>
        </article>

        <article class="partner-impact-tile partner-soft-shadow">
          <div class="partner-impact-icon partner-impact-icon-teal" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M19.43 12.98c.04-.32.07-.64.07-.98 0-.34-.03-.66-.07-.98l2.11-1.65a.5.5 0 00.12-.64l-2-3.46a.5.5 0 00-.61-.22l-2.49 1a7.03 7.03 0 00-1.7-.98l-.38-2.65A.5.5 0 0014 2h-4a.5.5 0 00-.49.42l-.38 2.65c-.62.24-1.21.56-1.7.98l-2.49-1a.5.5 0 00-.61.22l-2 3.46a.5.5 0 00.12.64l2.11 1.65c-.04.32-.07.65-.07.98 0 .34.03.66.07.98l-2.11 1.65a.5.5 0 00-.12.64l2 3.46c.14.24.43.32.69.22l2.49-1c.49.42 1.08.74 1.7.98l.38 2.65c.04.24.24.42.49.42h4c.25 0 .45-.18.49-.42l.38-2.65c.62-.24 1.21-.56 1.7-.98l2.49 1c.26.1.55.02.69-.22l2-3.46a.5.5 0 00-.12-.64l-2.11-1.65zM12 15.5A3.5 3.5 0 1112 8.5a3.5 3.5 0 010 7z"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <span>Systems</span>
        </article>

        <article class="partner-impact-feature">
          <div class="partner-impact-feature-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M9.19 6.35c-2.04 2.29-3.44 5.58-3.57 5.89L2 10.69l4.05-4.05c.47-.47 1.15-.68 1.81-.55l1.33.26zm5.62 0l1.33-.26c.66-.13 1.34.08 1.81.55L22 10.69l-3.62 1.55c-.13-.31-1.53-3.6-3.57-5.89zM12 4c-4.97 0-9 4.03-9 9 0 4.17 2.84 7.67 6.69 8.69L12 22l2.31-2.31C18.16 18.67 21 15.17 21 13c0-4.97-4.03-9-9-9zm0 2c3.87 0 7 3.13 7 7 0 1.53-.49 2.94-1.33 4.09L12 20.59 6.33 17.1C5.49 15.94 5 14.53 5 13c0-3.87 3.13-7 7-7z"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Tech &amp; Infrastructure</h3>
          <p>Deploying digital platforms and business systems to entrepreneurship clusters across Zambia.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="partner-form-section" id="partner-form">
    <div class="container">
      <header class="partner-form-intro">
        <h2>Start a Conversation</h2>
        <p>Fill out the form below and our partnership team will reach out within 48 hours.</p>
      </header>

      <form class="partner-form" method="POST" action="/partner" novalidate>
        <% if (sent) { %>
        <div class="partner-alert partner-alert-success" role="status">Thank you. Your partnership interest has been received.</div>
        <% } %>
        <% if (error) { %>
        <div class="partner-alert partner-alert-error" role="alert"><%= error %></div>
        <% } %>

        <div class="partner-form-field">
          <label for="partner-name">Full Name</label>
          <input id="partner-name" name="name" type="text" required placeholder="John Doe" value="<%= form.name || '' %>" autocomplete="name" />
        </div>

        <div class="partner-form-field">
          <label for="partner-organization">Organization</label>
          <input id="partner-organization" name="organization" type="text" placeholder="Company or NGO Name" value="<%= form.organization || '' %>" autocomplete="organization" />
        </div>

        <div class="partner-form-field">
          <label for="partner-email">Email Address</label>
          <input id="partner-email" name="email" type="email" required placeholder="email@example.com" value="<%= form.email || '' %>" autocomplete="email" />
        </div>

        <div class="partner-form-row">
          <div class="partner-form-field">
            <label for="partner-country">Country</label>
            <select id="partner-country" name="country">
              <% const countries = ['Zambia', 'South Africa', 'United Kingdom', 'USA', 'Other']; %>
              <% countries.forEach(function(c) { %>
              <option value="<%= c %>"<%= (form.country || 'Zambia') === c ? ' selected' : '' %>><%= c %></option>
              <% }); %>
            </select>
          </div>
          <div class="partner-form-field">
            <label for="partner-interest">Interest</label>
            <select id="partner-interest" name="interest">
              <% const interests = ['Donation Support', 'Strategic Partnership', 'Technical Support', 'Business Mentorship', 'NGO / Donor Collaboration', 'Other']; %>
              <% const selectedInterest = form.interest || 'Donation Support'; %>
              <% interests.forEach(function(i) { %>
              <option value="<%= i %>"<%= selectedInterest === i ? ' selected' : '' %>><%= i %></option>
              <% }); %>
            </select>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="partner-form-field">
          <label for="partner-message">Message</label>
          <textarea id="partner-message" name="message" required placeholder="Tell us how you would like to collaborate..." rows="4"><%= form.message || '' %></textarea>
        </div>

        <div class="partner-form-actions">
          <button class="partner-btn partner-btn-primary" type="submit">Submit Proposal</button>
          <a href="/contact" class="partner-btn partner-btn-outline">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 15.5c-1.25 0-2.45-.2-3.57-.57a1.02 1.02 0 00-1.02.24l-2.2 2.2a15.045 15.045 0 01-6.59-6.59l2.2-2.21a.96.96 0 00.25-1A11.36 11.36 0 018.5 4c0-.55-.45-1-1-1H4c-.55 0-1 .45-1 1 0 9.39 7.61 17 17 17 .55 0 1-.45 1-1v-3.5c0-.55-.45-1-1-1z"></path></svg>
            Contact Us Directly
          </a>
        </div>
      </form>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="partner-donate">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="partner-donate-card partner-soft-shadow">
        <div class="partner-donate-glow" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <h2>Donation Interest</h2>
        <p>
          Don't have time for a full partnership? Share your support interest below and Moovex will contact
          you with the appropriate details. There is no online payment on this site.
        </p>
        <div class="partner-donate-amounts">
          <a href="#partner-form" class="partner-donate-amount">General support</a>
          <a href="#partner-form" class="partner-donate-amount">Project support</a>
          <a href="#partner-form" class="partner-donate-amount">Support inquiry</a>
        </div>
        <a href="#partner-form" class="partner-btn partner-btn-dark">Express Donation Interest</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>

<%- include('../partials/footer') %>
<script src="/js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
